  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>The hotel is on a half board basis. Please note, the restaurant is closed on Wednesday evenings, so dinner is only available for six nights of your stay - the perfect opportunity to eat out in resort and try some of the local cuisine.</p>
<p>The continental breakfast buffet and hot options is served between 7:30 - 10am. Dinner is three courses with a choice of two starters, two choices of main course and then to finish a choice of cheeses or dessert.</p>]]></cateringDescription>
