  <description><![CDATA[<p>Hotel Les Trois Vallees has wonderful views over the slopes and mountains and it couldn't be easier to begin your skiing day as the slopes are right on your doorstep. The boutique style of this hotel makes it a great choice for couples and small families or groups of friends.</p>
<h2>Family run hotel </h2>
<p>Run by the Gorini family since 1979, Les Trois Vallées is a cosy, friendly hotel with an enviable reputation for high standards of comfort and service - so we can assure you that you and your family will be looked after well. </p>
<h2>Food and drink </h2>
<p>There's no better way to spend your holiday then enjoying great meals and socialising over drinks with the mountains as your background. Inspired by the Olympic Games, the hotels restaurant 'L'Olympiski' invites you to try traditional French cuisine, mountain specialities and fresh home-made desserts. You'll also have access to the bar &amp; lounge area where you can relax with a variety of snacks, wines and cocktail hour. </p>
<h2>Attractive interior </h2>
<p>Whether you're here on your own or part of a group, this hotel offers modern, spacious bedrooms that will meet your every need. Each room is made with wood from old alpine farms creating a desirable and traditional mountain atmosphere. </p>
<p> </p>]]></description>
