  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Double 'Cocoon' Rooms</strong> are around 14-16m² sleeping two with twin or double beds. These rooms have a piste view and a shower in the en-suite. These rooms are also available for sole occupancy on request, please give our Reservations agents a call to book.</p>
<p><strong>Double 'Cocoon' Veranda Rooms</strong> are around 16 to 21m² sleeping two with twin or double beds, a seating area and a shower in the en-suite. These rooms are also available for sole occupancy on request, please give our Reservations agents a call to book.</p>
<p><strong>Family Quad Rooms</strong> are around 26m² sleeping up to four people. These rooms have a double bed, and bunk beds in a separate corner. These rooms have a bath with shower head attachment and a separate WC. </p>
<p><strong>Superior Triple Rooms</strong> are around 23m² sleeping three people. This room has one double bed and a single bed (side by side). The en-suite has a bath with shower head attachment and a separate WC.</p>
<p><strong>Privilege Suites</strong> are around 29-33m² sleeping two. These rooms have a bedroom with double bed and a sofa bed in the lounge area. The en-suite has a jacuzzi bathtub, shower and separate WC. Then either a sauna or hammam (please specify your preference when booking). Triple Privilege Suites are available on request, please give our Reservations team a call to book.</p>
<p><strong>Bedroom facilities</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Twin or double bed (please specify your preference when booking; Suites only have double beds)</li>
<li>En-suite with WC</li>
<li>TV</li>
<li>Wi-Fi</li>
<li>Safe</li>
<li>Bathrobes on request</li>
<li>Towels</li>
<li>Hairdryer</li>
<li>Radio</li>
<li>Views of the pistes</li>
<li>Cots are available on request</li>
</ul>
<p> </p>]]></roomsDescription>
